 close. The next fall-throughs are optional prompt-toolkit input with slash-command completion (descriptions through `display_meta`), explicit file/path completion, completion-only `@file` reference l
abels, and multiline entry; then the stdlib `readline` adapter for Tab discovery without a runtime dependency; then plain stdin/stderr for captured streams. Richer editor behavior (history, resize-res
ilient TUI, mouse selection) remains deferred. |[0m
